data.description: Come See this expansive split-level home!  There's plenty of space! Four sides of brick and comes complete with a fully finished basement-new flooring just installed!  Inside, you'll discover a welcoming open kitchen concept seamlessly connected to the family room, offering a delightful view and featuring a charming brick fireplace for added coziness. The lower level offers additional space, including two bedrooms, a bonus room, and a full bathroom. Step outside to find an extended deck and a patio, perfect for both entertaining and relaxation. There's even a convenient storage shed and a basketball court to enhance your outdoor experience. This home would be perfect for the first time home buyer or the client looking to run a group home. Home is nestled on a generous 0.47-acre lot featuring a fenced backyard within a tranquil and long-established neighborhood. Ample parking is at your disposal with a carport, driveway, and parking pad. The property's location ensures easy access to I-20, local schools, Arbor Place Mall, Sweetwater Creek State Park, the airport, and all the vibrant attractions of Atlanta. Don't miss the opportunity to call this home!!
